724933f-a.title: Manhattan: York Street - St. John's Lane
724933f-a.text:
2 York Street, at the S.E. corner of St. John's Lane. Also shown
is st. John's Lane, east side, south from and including York to, but
not including Beach Streets. Building concerned is a 3-story frame
hhouse.
December 7, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
